txt.en: War-Tyrant Akúlhun waits your return to Gramsfoot where he will see you rewarded for your service to Tirith Rhaw!
You have been recognized as a servant to the master of Tirith Rhaw!
'Another servant to Angmar! You are recognized this day with a reward long due. Use it well, maggot!'
Service to the master of Tirith Rhaw will result in the ability to find your way to the tower with less effort.
Complete quests for the benefit of Tirith Rhaw!
You have performed many services for the master of Lugazag.
